<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>About Us - Ecommerce Outlaws</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
      :root {
        --primary: #001f3f;
        --secondary: #00b894;
        --text-dark: #222;
        --light-gray: #f8f9fa;
        --white: #ffffff;
      }

      body {
        font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
        color: var(--text-dark);
        background-color: var(--white);
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .navbar {
        background-color: var(--primary);
        box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0, 31, 63, 0.1);
      }

      .navbar-brand, .nav-link {
        color: white !important;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      /* ENHANCED ANIMATIONS */
      @keyframes fadeInUp {
        from {
          opacity: 0;
          transform: translateY(30px);
        }
        to {
          opacity: 1;
          transform: translateY(0);
        }
      }

      @keyframes slideInLeft {
        from {
          opacity: 0;
          transform: translateX(-50px);
        }
        to {
          opacity: 1;
          transform: translateX(0);
        }
      }

      @keyframes slideInRight {
        from {
          opacity: 0;
          transform: translateX(50px);
        }
        to {
          opacity: 1;
          transform: translateX(0);
        }
      }

      @keyframes pulse {
        0%, 100% {
          transform: scale(1);
        }
        50% {
          transform: scale(1.05);
        }
      }

      @keyframes shimmer {
        0% {
          background-position: -200% 0;
        }
        100% {
          background-position: 200% 0;
        }
      }

      /* SCROLL ANIMATIONS */
      .animate-on-scroll {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(30px);
        transition: all 0.8s ease-out;
      }

      .animate-on-scroll.animated {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }

      .animate-left {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateX(-50px);
        transition: all 0.8s ease-out;
      }

      .animate-left.animated {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateX(0);
      }

      .animate-right {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateX(50px);
        transition: all 0.8s ease-out;
      }

      .animate-right.animated {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateX(0);
      }

      /* ENHANCED HERO SECTION */
      .hero-about {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 31, 63, 0.7) 0%, rgba(0, 31, 63, 0.5) 100%), url('/images/hero4.jpg');
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        background-attachment: fixed;
        color: white;
        height: 85vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        animation: heroGlow 6s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
      }

      @keyframes heroGlow {
        0% { 
          box-shadow: inset 0 0 100px rgba(0, 31, 63, 0.3), 0 0 50px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.1);
        }
        100% { 
          box-shadow: inset 0 0 100px rgba(0, 31, 63, 0.1), 0 0 50px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.2);
        }
      }

      .hero-about::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><defs><pattern id="grain" width="100" height="100" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><circle cx="25" cy="25" r="1" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/><circle cx="75" cy="75" r="1" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.05)"/></pattern></defs><rect width="100" height="100" fill="url(%23grain)"/></svg>');
        opacity: 0.3;
        animation: twinkle 4s ease-in-out infinite;
      }

      @keyframes twinkle {
        0%, 100% { opacity: 0.2; }
        50% { opacity: 0.4; }
      }

      .hero-about .container {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
      }

      .hero-about h1 {
        font-size: 4rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        text-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        animation: titleGlow 3s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ffffff, #e3f2fd, #ffffff);
        background-size: 200% 200%;
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
      }

      @keyframes titleFloat {
        0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
        50% { transform: translateY(-8px); }
      }

      @keyframes titleGlow {
        0% { filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3)); }
        100% { filter: drop-shadow(0 0 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6)); }
      }

      .hero-about .lead {
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        font-weight: 400;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        opacity: 0.9;
        animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 0.5s both;
      }

      .hero-stats {
        margin-top: 3rem;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 3rem;
        animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 1s both;
      }

      .hero-stat {
        text-align: center;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }

      .hero-stat:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
      }

      .hero-stat h3 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        color: white;
        text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        animation: pulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
      }

      .hero-stat:hover h3 {
        transform: scale(1.15);
        text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8), 0 0 60px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.4);
        animation-play-state: paused;
      }

      .hero-stat p {
        font-size: 1rem;
        opacity: 0.8;
        margin: 0;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }

      .hero-stat:hover p {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }

      /* ENHANCED CONTENT SECTIONS */
      .about-section {
        padding: 80px 0;
      }

      .about-section.alt {
        background-color: var(--light-gray);
      }

      .section-title {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--primary);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .section-title::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        bottom: -5px;
        left: 50%;
        width: 60px;
        height: 3px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary), #0066cc);
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        border-radius: 2px;
        animation: lineGlow 2s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
      }

      @keyframes lineGlow {
        0% { 
          box-shadow: 0 0 5px var(--primary);
          width: 60px;
        }
        100% { 
          box-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--primary), 0 0 25px rgba(0, 31, 63, 0.3);
          width: 80px;
        }
      }

      .section-subtitle {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: #6c757d;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
      }

      .content-card {
        background: white;
        padding: 25px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 31, 63, 0.08);
        border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        height: 100%;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .content-card::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: -100%;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(0, 31, 63, 0.1), transparent);
        transition: left 0.6s ease;
      }

      .content-card:hover::before {
        left: 100%;
      }

      .content-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.02);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 31, 63, 0.15);
        border-color: var(--primary);
      }

      .content-card h3 {
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--primary);
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }

      .content-card:hover h3 {
        color: #0066cc;
        transform: translateX(5px);
      }

      .content-card p {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }

      .content-card:hover p {
        color: var(--text-dark);
      }

      .icon-box {
        width: 60px;
        height: 60px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #0066cc);
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        margin: 0 auto 1.2rem;
        color: white;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        transition: all 0.4s ease;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .icon-box::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        width: 0;
        height: 0;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        border-radius: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }

      .content-card:hover .icon-box {
        transform: rotateY(180deg) scale(1.1);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 31, 63, 0.3);
      }

      .content-card:hover .icon-box::before {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
      }

      /* ENHANCED TIMELINE */
      .timeline {
        position: relative;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .timeline::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        left: 50%;
        top: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        width: 3px;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--primary), #0066cc, var(--primary));
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 31, 63, 0.3);
        animation: timelinePulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
      }

      @keyframes timelinePulse {
        0%, 100% { 
          box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 31, 63, 0.3);
          background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--primary), #0066cc, var(--primary));
        }
        50% { 
          box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 31, 63, 0.5), 0 0 30px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.2);
          background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0066cc, var(--primary), #0066cc);
        }
      }

      .timeline-item {
        position: relative;
        margin: 3rem 0;
      }

      .timeline-content {
        background: white;
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 15px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 31, 63, 0.1);
        position: relative;
        width: 45%;
        transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
      }

      .timeline-content::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, transparent, rgba(0, 31, 63, 0.05), transparent);
        border-radius: 15px;
        opacity: 0;
        transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
      }

      .timeline-content:hover::before {
        opacity: 1;
      }

      .timeline-content:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px) scale(1.02);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 31, 63, 0.15);
        border-color: var(--primary);
      }

      .timeline-item:nth-child(odd) .timeline-content {
        margin-left: auto;
        text-align: right;
      }

      .timeline-item:nth-child(even) .timeline-content {
        margin-right: auto;
        text-align: left;
      }

      .timeline-date {
        position: absolute;
        left: 50%;
        top: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #0066cc);
        color: white;
        padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
        border-radius: 25px;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        white-space: nowrap;
        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 31, 63, 0.3);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        animation: dateFloat 4s ease-in-out infinite;
      }

      @keyframes dateFloat {
        0%, 100% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) translateY(0px); }
        50% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) translateY(-3px); }
      }

      .timeline-date:hover {
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.1);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 31, 63, 0.4);
      }

      .timeline-content h4 {
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--primary);
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }

      .timeline-content:hover h4 {
        color: #0066cc;
        transform: translateX(5px);
      }

      /* ENHANCED VALUES GRID */
      .values-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-top: 3rem;
      }

      .value-card {
        background: white;
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 12px;
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 31, 63, 0.08);
        border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .value-card::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: -50%;
        left: -50%;
        width: 200%;
        height: 200%;
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 31, 63, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
        transform: scale(0);
        transition: transform 0.6s ease;
      }

      .value-card:hover::before {
        transform: scale(1);
      }

      .value-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-10px) rotateY(5deg);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 31, 63, 0.15);
        border-color: var(--primary);
      }

      .value-card .icon {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        color: var(--primary);
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        transition: all 0.4s ease;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .value-card:hover .icon {
        color: #0066cc;
        transform: scale(1.2) rotateY(360deg);
        text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 31, 63, 0.3);
      }

      .value-card h4 {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--primary);
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .value-card:hover h4 {
        color: #0066cc;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }

      .value-card p {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }

      .value-card:hover p {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }

      /* ENHANCED CTA SECTION */
      .cta-section {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #003366, #0066cc);
        background-size: 200% 200%;
        color: white;
        padding: 80px 0;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        animation: gradientShift 6s ease-in-out infinite;
      }

      @keyframes gradientShift {
        0%, 100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
        50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
      }

      .cta-section::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><defs><pattern id="stars" width="20" height="20" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><circle cx="10" cy="10" r="1" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/><circle cx="5" cy="5" r="0.5" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.05)"/></pattern></defs><rect width="100" height="100" fill="url(%23stars)"/></svg>');
        opacity: 0.3;
        animation: starTwinkle 8s ease-in-out infinite;
      }

      @keyframes starTwinkle {
        0%, 100% { opacity: 0.2; transform: translateX(0); }
        50% { opacity: 0.4; transform: translateX(10px); }
      }

      .cta-section .container {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
      }

      .cta-section h2 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        animation: titleGlow 3s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
      }

      .cta-section p {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        opacity: 0.9;
        animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 0.3s both;
      }

      .btn-outline-light {
        padding: 12px 30px;
        font-weight: 600;
        border: 2px solid white;
        border-radius: 50px;
        transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 0.6s both;
      }

      .btn-outline-light::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        width: 0;
        height: 0;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border-radius: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }

      .btn-outline-light:hover::before {
        width: 300px;
        height: 300px;
      }

      .btn-outline-light:hover {
        background: white;
        color: var(--primary);
        transform: translateY(-5px) scale(1.05);
        box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        border-color: white;
      }

      /* RESPONSIVE */
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .hero-about h1 {
          font-size: 2.5rem;
        }
        
        .hero-stats {
          flex-direction: column;
          gap: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .timeline::before {
          left: 2rem;
        }
        
        .timeline-content {
          width: calc(100% - 4rem);
          margin-left: 4rem !important;
          text-align: left !important;
        }
        
        .timeline-date {
          left: 2rem;
          transform: translateY(-50%);
        }

        .value-card:hover {
          transform: translateY(-5px) rotateY(0deg);
        }

        .content-card:hover {
          transform: translateY(-5px) scale(1.01);
        }
      }

      /* ADDITIONAL SCROLL ANIMATIONS */
      .fade-in-up {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(30px);
        transition: all 0.8s ease-out;
      }

      .fade-in-up.visible {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }

      .slide-in-left {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateX(-50px);
        transition: all 0.8s ease-out;
      }

      .slide-in-left.visible {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateX(0);
      }

      .slide-in-right {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateX(50px);
        transition: all 0.8s ease-out;
      }

      .slide-in-right.visible {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateX(0);
      }

      /* LOADING ANIMATIONS */
      @keyframes scaleIn {
        from {
          opacity: 0;
          transform: scale(0.8);
        }
        to {
          opacity: 1;
          transform: scale(1);
        }
      }

      .scale-in {
        animation: scaleIn 0.6s ease-out;
      }

      /* HOVER GLOW EFFECTS */
      .glow-on-hover {
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }

      .glow-on-hover:hover {
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 31, 63, 0.3), 0 0 40px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.1);
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <!-- ✅ HERO SECTION -->
    <section class="hero-about">
      <div class="container text-center">
        <h1>About US</h1>
        <p class="lead">Breaking fashion rules since day one. Built for rebels, worn by legends.</p>
        <div class="hero-stats">
          <div class="hero-stat">
            <h3>2020</h3>
            <p>Founded</p>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-stat">
            <h3>50K+</h3>
            <p>Happy Customers</p>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-stat">
            <h3>500+</h3>
            <p>Products</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ✅ WHO WE ARE -->
    <section class="about-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Who We Are</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">We're not just another fashion brand. We're a movement of style rebels who refuse to follow the crowd.</p>
        
        <div class="row g-4">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="content-card">
              <div class="icon-box">
                <i class="fas fa-fire"></i>
              </div>
              <h3>Style Rebels</h3>
              <p>We believe fashion should be fearless. Every piece in our collection is designed for those who dare to stand out, make statements, and break conventional style rules.</p>
              <p>From streetwear essentials to bold statement pieces, we create clothing that empowers you to express your true self without compromise.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="content-card">
              <div class="icon-box">
                <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
              </div>
              <h3>Community Driven</h3>
              <p>Our community of outlaws spans across the globe. We're connected by a shared belief that fashion is personal, powerful, and should never be dictated by trends alone.</p>
              <p>Every design decision we make is influenced by feedback from our community of style rebels who aren't afraid to push boundaries.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ✅ OUR JOURNEY -->
    <section class="about-section alt">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Our Journey</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">From a bold idea to a global fashion movement</p>
        
        <div class="timeline">
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-date">2020</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h4>The Beginning</h4>
              <p>Started with a simple mission: create fashion for people who refuse to blend in. Our first collection launched with just 10 pieces but unlimited attitude.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-date">2021</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h4>Breaking Ground</h4>
              <p>Expanded our reach globally and introduced our signature "Outlaw" line. Our community grew to over 10,000 style rebels worldwide.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-date">2023</div>
